& [SLMLMStudioResponseValidationRepairContract] is the contract for defensive sidecar response parsing
  + [contract_uuid] is 64f9217b-eed7-4ab4-a179-3799682a049f
  + [slice_id] is SLM-54
  + [depends_on] is SLM_LM_Studio_Sidecar_Adapter_Contract, SLM_Sidecar_Task_Prompt_Contract
  + [status] is verified_wsl

  & [Purpose] is to prevent malformed sidecar output from entering evidence as trusted graph support
    = must: accept exact JSON matching LmStudioProviderSuggestionResponse
    = must: repair JSON fenced in markdown when the inner JSON is valid
    = must: repair a top-level provider suggestion array by wrapping it in provider_suggestions
    = must: reject freeform or unparseable output
    = must: convert rejected output into a provider objection when caller supplies provenance and target
    - never: infer ProviderSuggestion content from prose outside JSON
    - never: create glyphs, graph relations, or candidate meanings from malformed sidecar output

  & [ValidationStatuses] are the parser outcomes
    + [accepted] is exact structured JSON
    + [repaired] is structurally repaired JSON with repair notes
    + [rejected] is untrusted output represented only as objection evidence

  & [RuntimeProjection] is the Rust source surface
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs SidecarResponseValidationStatus
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs SidecarValidatedParseOutcome
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs parse_lm_studio_provider_suggestions_validated
    + [module] is slm_rust/src/sidecar.rs rejection_objection
    + [proof_route] is parser tests and WSL cargo test

  ! [Slice54SourceComplete] is accepted
    @ [source_gate] passed python slm_project/tools/slm_source_gate_check.py
    @ [wsl_cargo_test] passed 26 library tests and 3 slm_demo tests
    @ [regression_harness] passed slm_regression_harness_ok
    @ [parser_accepts] exact provider_suggestions JSON
    @ [parser_repairs] fenced top-level provider suggestion array JSON
    @ [parser_rejects] freeform text as lineage_gap objection evidence without graph meaning
